import React from 'react' import '../styles/tour-details.css'; import {Container,Row,Col,Form,ListGroup} from 'reactstrap' import {useParams} from 'react-router-dom' import tourData from '../assets/data/tours' import calculateAvgRating from '../utils/avgRating'; import avatar from '../assets/images/avatar' const TourDetails = () => { //call api later to load data from db const {id} = useParams() const tour = tourData.find(tour=>tour.id === id) //destructure props for tour object const {photo,title,address,price,reviews,city,distance,maxGroupSize,desc} = tour const {totalRating,avgRating} = calculateAvgRating(reviews) return <>

{title}

{calculateAvgRating ===0? null:avgRating}{totalRating===0?('Not rated'):( ({reviews.length}) )} {address}
{city} ${price}/per person {maxGroupSize}
Description

{desc}

Reviews({reviews?.length} reviews)

1 2 3 4 5
{ reviews?.map(review=>(
)) }
} export default TourDetails
